SELECT COALESCE("QUESTIONID", "QUESTIONID") AS "QUESTIONID", "QUESTIONSCORE", "QUESTIONVIEWS", "ANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "$f7" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("$f7" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "AVERAGEANSWERSCORE", CASE WHEN "$f8" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("$f8" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "AVERAGEANSWERVIEWS"
FROM (SELECT "Id0", "Score0", "ViewCount0", ANY_VALUE("Id0") AS "QUESTIONID", ANY_VALUE("Score0") AS "QUESTIONSCORE", ANY_VALUE("ViewCount0") AS "QUESTIONVIEWS", COUNT("Id") AS "ANSWERCOUNT", AVG("Score") AS "$f7", AVG("ViewCount") AS "$f8"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "Id0", "Score0", "ViewCount0"
ORDER BY 4) AS "t2"